      <h2>3. User Content</h2>
      <p>By posting content on our platform, you grant us a non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, and distribute that content.</p>
      
      <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on Shopperqueries, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of Shopperqueries and protected by copyright laws.</p>
      
      <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Shopperqueries is not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of our service.</p>
      
      <h2>6. Disclaimer</h2>
